    "A C++ and Java developer by profession, but a Swift and Haskell hobbyist. I'm passionate about building things that make a positive impact on people's lives, and try to learn new things when I have free time. I am a practicing zen and stoic philosopher, love to read, and am an avid enjoyer of games (Death Stranding, Warhammer 40k, Civ, Stellaris, Arcs (board game). I was frustrated that there wasn't a native GitLab client for my phone, so figued...why not make one? Thank you for checking out Grit, and I hope you will find it useful <3" : {
